ch.nolix.core.container

Class Matrix<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.nolix.core.container.Matrix<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of the elements of a Matrix.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IContainer<E>, Clearable<Matrix<E>>, java.lang.Iterable<E>

    public final class Matrix<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IContainer<E>, Clearable<Matrix<E>>
    A Matrix is a IContainer that stores its elements in rows and columns. A Matrix is clearable.
    Author:
    Silvan Wyss
